{"tid":115011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網友要哭了！A片頁面在俄羅斯遭禁　政府解釋：傷害人民心靈","createTime":"2017-02-10T08:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T19:16:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c33202f5243a871e03058fb6391b3fc7b9b752e","tid":115011,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=223081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D223081&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=fe612917\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D223081&h=78217875\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=223081</a><br />\n俄羅斯政府去年才查禁全球最大的色情網站Pornhub（<a href=\"http://www.pornhub.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pornhub.com&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1a2ce218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.pornhub.com</a> ），近日又以「對人民心靈產生嚴重負面影響」為由，封鎖A片網站Brazzers（<a href=\"http://www.brazzers.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brazzers.com%2F&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b3e0ccbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.brazzers.com/</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n根據《莫斯科時報》報導，俄羅斯政府高層認為這些網站對兒童有害，除了親自下「禁A令」，還陸續將色情網站查禁，並稱Brazzers「嚴重侵犯公民的權利」，伺服器目前已停止連上該網站，用戶若試圖開啟網頁，將被告知「無法瀏覽這些不合法的內容」。Brazzers位於加拿大的總公司尚未有任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2017/02/08/803274-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F803274-XXL.jpg&h=bf5aadcb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n▲俄羅斯政府將色情網站Brazzers封鎖。（圖／翻攝自Brazzers官網）"},{"pid":"8ae6031d859e0bb305f648ccfe5b523c020dd2f2","tid":115011,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"應該就打Civil war"},{"pid":"c476412c